Install Fuse.pm, using aptitude/apt-get:
$ aptitude install libfuse-perl;

DBIx::Schema might need to be installed manually:
$ wget 'http://search.cpan.org/CPAN/authors/id/J/JM/JMAC/DBIx-Schema-0.07.tar.gz'
$ tar xfz DBIx-Schema-0.07.tar.gz
$ cd DBIx-Schema-0.07
$ perl Makefile.PL
# press enter on all questions
$ make install
